00:19:31,248 --> 00:19:32,128
I would be getting back data,

472
00:19:32,128 --> 00:19:34,089
and this feels more real to me.

473
00:19:34,089 --> 00:19:36,851
So again, like a strong decision that we decided to make

474
00:19:36,851 --> 00:19:39,071
so that everything is going in the same direction

475
00:19:39,071 --> 00:19:41,312
and everything is revolving around this realism pillar.

476
00:19:41,312 --> 00:19:42,213
Right?

477
00:19:42,213 --> 00:19:43,253
So did this come across?

478
00:19:43,654 --> 00:19:45,215
I would say that it did.

