00:19:45,215 --> 00:19:47,036
We got so many people, all of our fans,

480
00:19:47,036 --> 00:19:49,878
they put on headphones, they turn off the lights,

481
00:19:49,878 --> 00:19:50,899
and the monitor is their monitor,

482
00:19:50,899 --> 00:19:52,540
and they imagine they're in a spaceship.

